description:
Upromise by Sallie Mae is an innovative service that helps its members earn money back for college from their everyday spending. So far Upromise members have received more than $600 million in college savings. It costs nothing to join. 

- To start saving, become a Upromise member and begin earning contributions with our contributing companies. 
- Once you join Upromise, every time you make an eligible purchase, our partners return a portion of that money back to you. 
- The money you earn from your everyday spending with Upromise partners goes directly into your Upromise account. 

The Upromise mobile application can help you find restaurants, retail stores and gas stations that are part of the Upromise service. 

- The Upromise mobile app can provide helpful information based on your location. 
- Search for merchants and restaurants by location or browse by categories to see the results in a list view or on a map. 
- Once you find restaurants and merchants in your area, be sure to review the merchant details and ensure that your purchase will be eligible for Upromise rewards. 
- Add merchants and restaurants to your favorites and enjoy anytime access to favorites, even when you’re offline. 
- Share merchants with your friends via email, Facebook or Twitter. 

Upcoming capabilities:
- Access to your current Upromise account balance. 
- Grocery eCoupons for participating grocery and drug stores.

Your use of the Upromise mobile application is subject to the Upromise privacy statement. Learn more at: http://www.upromise.com/welcome/details/privacy
